parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: airbag fails to deploy in a crash
passenger airbag is always lit (off) when the ignition is turned on
airbag indicator light comes on intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to provide timely and effective recall repairs can lead to continued risk of airbag failure.
symptoms: dealer unable to schedule recall repair
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair
airbag light stays on after recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to false warnings, unnecessary repairs, and continued risk of airbag failure.
symptoms: passenger airbag is always lit (off) when the ignition is turned on
airbag indicator light comes on intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The uncomfortable and painful seats can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and may also lead to long-term back and leg problems.
The failure of the active head restraints can lead to injuries in the event of a collision, as they may not provide adequate support to the head and neck.
symptoms: The active head restraints move into the forward position without reason
and do not return to their normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering rack can cause loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to drive the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: fluid leaking from the rack and pinion

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission problems can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: speeding up and down without driver input

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the VSA modulator can cause the vehicle to lose stability and traction, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Warning lights for ABS and stability control

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system issues can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
SRS light issues can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or death.
